data.description: Immaculate and completely updated POOL home!!! This beautiful, move in ready home offers 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, 1368 sqft, oversized 1 car garage, LANAI, and a privacy FENCED YARD. Everything is NEW!  Kitchen 2022, Bathrooms 2022, Roof 2022, AC 2022, Windows 2022, Water Heater, 2022, Solar Panels 2023, Floors 2022, Lights, Blinds, Ceiling Fans - 2022, French Doors 2022, Shower Door 2022, Solar Pool Pump 2023, interior and exterior paint 2022 and New Vinyl privacy fence 2022. Plenty of storage in the 19x24 456 sqft garage. Enjoy outside entertaining next to the sparkling pool in the 18x21 screened and covered lanai, on the pool deck or the spacious private backyard. The gorgeous kitchen is the heart of the home and has new cabinets, granite counters, a large closet pantry, and a spacious breakfast bar. There is a breakfast nook area that is perfect for a small table or your coffee bar. The dining room is light and bright and opens to the kitchen area. Easy access to 378 sqft lanai through French doors off the kitchen. Lots of space to entertain inside as well! The living room is 21x11 and could be separated into a formal area and family room area if you would like. The master suite offers sliders to the lanai and a walk-in closet. The remodeled bathroom has a walk-in shower and beautiful tile. The secondary bedrooms have plenty of closet space. The front patio boasts a nice covered sitting area. Enjoy the extra driveway space with the extended driveway to accommodate multiple cars. NO HOA!! Convenient to Tarpon Springs Sponge Docks, restaurants, Anclote Park and boat ramp, beaches, shopping, and medical facilities.
